        <item>
            <title>WhatsApp 新四大編輯訊息功能　可選擇文字直接編輯</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/whatsapp-20/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=whatsapp-20</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/whatsapp-20/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:30:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[應用軟件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[WhatsApp]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221145</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">WhatsApp 更新推出四項新編輯文字訊息格式功能，可助用家整理文字，及提升用文字信息溝通的效率。現已適用於 Android、iOS、Web 及 Mac 桌面用家。用家需要將 WhatsApp 更新至最新版本 ，即可使用四大新編輯文字訊息格式功能。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221151 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3225-631x580.jpg" alt="" width="631" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3225-631x580.jpg 631w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3225.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 631px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221146 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3227-621x580.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3227-621x580.jpg 621w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3227.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 621px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iOS 用家可將 WhatsApp 更新至 24.4.3 版本</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>項目符號清單</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">用家只要輸入「-」及在後面輸入空格，即可獲得如食譜的格式，方便閲讀。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221147 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3221-689x580.jpg" alt="" width="689" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3221-689x580.jpg 689w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3221.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 689px" /></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>編號清單</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">有時想順序列出細項，過往就必須手動打上數字並分次序，現時只要在第一個項目上輸入「1.」並在後面多輸入一個空格，用家按下一行時，就會自動出現「2.」，不再手動輸入數字，條理更清晰。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221148 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3222-682x580.jpg" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3222-682x580.jpg 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3222.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/12/whatsapp-in-app-sticker-edit/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】WhatsApp 內自製貼圖，可在舊貼圖上畫公仔</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/whatsapp-to-sync-chat-locks-across-devices-for-enhanced-security/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 測試跨設備聊天鎖，提升訊息保安能力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/whatsapp-interoperability-messaging/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 準備加入跨平台互通支援　歐盟規定需要容許平台互通</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>引號</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">用家可輸入「&gt;」及一個空格，即可得到引號，方便用家引用其他文字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221149 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3223-694x530.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="530" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3223-694x530.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3223.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>行內代碼</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">此功能有助用家在分辨句子中的特別訊息，在輸入文字時可加上反引號「`」就可以了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221150 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3224-694x529.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="529" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3224-694x529.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3224.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">而舊有的功能，如粗體、斜體、刪除線及等寬字體選項，只要選擇文字就可直接編輯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221152 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3226-665x580.jpg" alt="" width="665" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3226-665x580.jpg 665w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img_3226.jpg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 665px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/12/whatsapp-in-app-sticker-edit/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】WhatsApp 內自製貼圖，可在舊貼圖上畫公仔</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/whatsapp-to-sync-chat-locks-across-devices-for-enhanced-security/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 測試跨設備聊天鎖，提升訊息保安能力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/whatsapp-interoperability-messaging/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 準備加入跨平台互通支援　歐盟規定需要容許平台互通</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/whatsapp-20/software/">WhatsApp 新四大編輯訊息功能　可選擇文字直接編輯</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
