        <item>
            <title>Stellantis 主動聲浪與震動新專利　創造模擬引擎體驗電動車</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/stellantis/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=stellantis</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/stellantis/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dodge Charger Daytona SRT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SRT Hellcat]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Stellantis]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[V8]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221074</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>不少剛換電動車的用家未能適應電動車異常的寧靜，欠缺了早已習慣的引擎震動和聲浪。Stellantis 為解決此問題，近日申請了主動聲浪與震動新專利，冀能創造模擬引擎體驗的純電車。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221089 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240222at-1-694x464.png" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240222at-1-694x464.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240222at-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Dodge Charger Daytona SRT 將加入主動音效增強裝置，模擬 V8 引擎聲浪</p><p>搭載大排量跑車或肌肉車，車主往往追求引擎聲，惟與電動車的寧靜則背道而馳。Stellantis 其下的 Dodge Charger Daytona SRT 就加入了主動聲浪系統，可以模擬出 SRT Hellcat 126 分貝的聲響。專利厲害之處，除了有聲響之外，引擎亦有明顯的震動。名為 ASE（主動音效增強裝置）的裝置是 Stellantis 準備替電動車裝上的新專利，通過精密感測器與整合控制器，再結合車主的油門和方向盤的力道、速度、角度，造出相對應的音效，最後由車內、車外喇叭及特別設計的排氣管低音喇叭，模擬 V8 引擎聲浪。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1221095 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240222at-2-694x461.png" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240222at-2-694x461.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/screenshot20240222at-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ASE（主動音效增強裝置）新專利</p><p>最新的 Stellantis 專利顯示，除了 ASE（主動音效增強裝置）外，亦會加添一個 AVE（主動震動增強裝置）。屆時用家更可感受到引擎震動感，更加完整地體驗 V8 引擎。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.carsales.com.au/editorial/details/stellantis-developing-vibrating-evs-to-mimic-hemi-v8-144702/">Carsales</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/stellantis/life-tech/auto/">Stellantis 主動聲浪與震動新專利　創造模擬引擎體驗電動車</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/stellantis/life-tech/auto/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《Contra: Operation Galuga》初代魂鬥羅重製版【有片睇】多平台推出試玩版</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[《Contra: Operation Galuga》]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[魂鬥羅]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221072</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>發行商 Konami 與開發商 WayForward 聯合宣佈，經典捲軸類射擊遊戲《魂鬥羅》將於 3 月 12 日於 Steam、PlayStation 5、PlayStation 4、Xbox Series、Xbox One 及 Switch 推出初代重製版《Contra: Operation Galuga》。實體版本於 3 月 1 日起可透過 Limited Run Games 預購。現時全部平台均已有試玩版讓玩家熱身，等待正式版推出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《Contra: Operation Galuga》是 80 年代經典捲軸射擊遊戲《魂鬥羅》的重製版，除了提升畫質、音效等，這次重製版亦加入了新的關卡、敵人、頭目、武器等。故事模式下最高支援 2 個玩家；街機模式則最高支援 4 個玩家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲故事模式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221117" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-3-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-3-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-3.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221118" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-4-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-4-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲是次加入了不少新的技能和武器</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/contra_operationgalu-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63156"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mIoyoDgBn9o?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mIoyoDgBn9o">Konami@YouTube</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/02/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available">Gematsu</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/contra-operation-galuga-launches-march-12-demo-now-available/game-channel/">《Contra: Operation Galuga》初代魂鬥羅重製版【有片睇】多平台推出試玩版</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
