        <item>
            <title>《GUNDAM Breaker4》今年登場，特典版情報全公開</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/gundam-breaker-4/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gundam-breaker-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/gundam-breaker-4/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gundam]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GUNDAM 創壞者 4]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221041</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>備受高達迷讚賞的以高達模型為主題的《GUNDAM Breaker》系列遊戲，將在今年推出第四集《GUNDAM Breaker 4》。是次會在 Nintendo Switch、PlayStation 5、PlayStation 4 及 STEAM 上登場。今日 BANDAI NAMCO 就同步公開各版本情報及首條宣傳影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/01-21-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/01-21-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/01-21.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221049" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/02-22-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/02-22-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/02-22.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>本作是動作遊戲《GUNDAM Breaker》系列之最新作，玩家可以在遊戲裏建造專屬於自己的「獨門高達模型」，並以其進行戰鬥。玩家在任務中打倒敵人獲得零件後，即可用來改裝自己的獨門高達模型。</p><p>在全新的「場景模型模式」中設定背景及特效等，製作專屬於自己的場景。<br />
盡情展現自己的獨門高達模型——</p><p>特點 1 「開創」：組合來自超過 250 架以上的機體零件，盡情改裝創造獨門高達模型。<br />
特點 2「戰鬥」：以獨門高達模型挑戰任務，打倒敵人即可獲得零件。<br />
特點 3 「展現」：設定背景、高達模型、特效等，建立專屬場景，並在完成後，拍攝精心設計的照片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221055" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/08-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/08-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/08.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>3 項全新進化</h2><p>①改裝進化：左右手可改裝為不同的零件或武器</p><p>在本作中，左右手可以分別設定為不同的零件，玩家將可以製作獨創性遠超過前作的獨門高達模型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221050" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-23-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-23-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-23.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221051" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-23-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-23-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-23.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>②動作進化：左右不同武裝為動作帶來大幅進化</p><p>使用裝備於右手及左手的武器與技能，打造專屬的連段攻擊。</p><p>玩家將可以配合眼前的情況分別使用右手及左手的武器，並透過技能組合，找到自己獨特的連段攻擊。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221052" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-17-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-17-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-17.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221053" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>③遊戲重點：利用全新的「場景模型模式」建造專屬場景</p><p>組合獨門高達模型、背景及各式各樣的物件，玩家將可打造屬於自己的場景。</p><p>更可於線上向其他玩家展示，獲得「Good Build」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221054" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/smpvoltesv/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】SMP《V 型電磁俠》　幾乎完全變形合體 + 另類關節設計高可動</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/14/gundam-seed-freedom/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《高達 SEED FREEDOM》日本票房超 26.8 億日元，高達劇場版票房最高 + YouTube 音樂祭直播慶祝</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2></h2><h2>特典、版本情報公開</h2><p><strong>實體版首批／數碼版預購共通特典</strong></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/09-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/09-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/09.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>首批購買實體版或預購數碼版的玩家，將可提前使用「高達（再循環配色）」完整零件組及製作人零件 6 種。</p><p><strong>Nintendo Switch／PlayStation5 版實體限定版</strong></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-co