            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>廣受歡迎的動作 RPG《Elden Ring》全新大型 DLC《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》將會在 6 月 21 日於全球同步發售。今日發佈首部預告片，讓各位玩家先睹為快。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221029" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/244screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/244screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/244screenshot.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/229screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/229screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/229screenshot.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》中，玩家將會踏入「幽影之地」，展開既神秘又充斥危險的全新冒險，並使用全新的武器及盔甲對抗極具威脅的頭目。追隨米凱拉的腳步，揭開《Elden Ring》故事中的黑暗秘密。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-22-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-22-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/03-22.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221032" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-22-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-22-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/04-22.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-16-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-16-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/05-16.png 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/06.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>公開版本情報</h2><p><strong>PlayStation 5／PlayStation 4 版實體限定版</strong></p><p>收錄內容：</p><ul><li>大型 DLC《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》下載代碼</li><li>「穿刺者」梅瑟莫角色模型（46 cm）</li><li>40 頁精裝美術書</li><li>數碼原聲帶</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221036" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07_tc-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07_tc-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/07_tc.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>PlayStation 5 版 Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree 版<br /></strong>實體版收錄內容：</p><ul><li>《艾爾登法環》實體遊戲光碟</li><li>大型 DLC《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》下載代碼</li></ul><p>數碼豪華版收錄內容：</p><ul><li>《Elden Ring》遊戲軟件</li><li>大型 DLC《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》</li><li>《Elden Ring》數碼美術書</li><li>《Elden Ring》數碼原聲帶</li><li>《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》數碼美術書</li><li>《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》數碼原聲帶</li></ul><p>數碼典藏包收錄內容：</p><ul><li>大型 DLC《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of the Erdtree》</li><li>《Elden Ring &#8211; Shadow of th